snippet.title: Fort Solis: Official Troy Baker Trailer
snippet.description: Troy Baker introduces the latest trailer for Fort Solis, the thriller starring Baker as Wyatt Taylor – alongside Roger Clark's Jack Leary and Julia Brown's Jessica Appleton – as players guide Leary through one long and terrifying night on Mars.
